Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaFF}…
Comment: 0,0:02:59.03,0:02:59.07,op jp,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:05.00,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}This is a fate that brought us here watch my long shot
Comment: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.56,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Feel like I am falling into the flame of lies
Comment: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.20,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Tell me what do you want from me
Comment: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.60,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Trying not to step back to where I used to belong
Comment: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.46,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Looking for the escape from pain
Comment: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:29.86,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I will cross my fingers hoping not to be sacrificed
Comment: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:33.30,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}約束したんだ君とその希望に
Comment: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:37.06,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Get in the raid Get ready for the time to come
Comment: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:40.60,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}浮かび上がるシルエット追いかけ
Comment: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.96,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Drop down the reason why I'm standing here alone
Comment: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:47.53,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}May be it's already too late to regain
Comment: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:52.90,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}運命としてかかげた灯を失くさないで
Comment: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.23,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Ever again
Comment: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:57.70,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}What if I could right my wrongs and save you from the pain
Comment: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.46,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}It's not enough
Comment: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:07.20,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}It's not enough for me to break the rule upon this world
Comment: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:12.23,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I will never gonna leave you never wanna lose you
Comment: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.56,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}we'll make it in the end
Comment: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:20.86,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Not backing down for real I won't trace someone else's life
Comment: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.23,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I know who I am
Comment: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:10.99,op ch,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:05.00,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}命運將我們引領至此 並看着我跳戰不可能
Comment: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.56,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}感覺我墮入了謊言的火焰中
Comment: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.20,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}說出你對我的要求
Comment: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.60,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}盡力不去走回頭路
Comment: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.46,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}探求走出痛苦的方法
Comment: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:29.86,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我合十雙手去祈求不必犧牲
Comment: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:33.30,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}這是我和你的希望所訂下的約定
Comment: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:37.06,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在時機成熟前做好出擊的準備
Comment: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:40.60,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}去追趕那個浮現出來的黑影
Comment: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.96,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}放棄那個讓我單獨一人的理由
Comment: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:47.53,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}或許這已經太遲
Comment: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:52.90,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不要捨去作為命運的那道光
Comment: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.23,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}沒有下次
Comment: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:57.70,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}若我能修補錯誤並將你救出苦海
Comment: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.46,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}這並不足以
Comment: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:07.20,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}並不足以讓我打破這世界的規則
Comment: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:12.23,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我絕不離開你 絕不想失去你
Comment: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.56,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我們來結束這一切
Comment: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:20.86,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}別再退縮 這輩子我不會跟隨別人
Comment: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.23,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我知道自己是誰
Comment: 0,0:27:30.04,0:27:30.08,ed jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.86,0:27:46.63,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}壊れないように優しく抱いて　溶けて涙流す
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.20,0:27:57.83,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}そんな氷の人形みたいに なれないから
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.26,0:28:12.06,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}もう逃げない　知りたいの　強く
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.06,0:28:13.76,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}―I believe…believe in you―
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.76,0:28:17.86,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}きっと一番の約束の言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.86,0:28:22.26,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}痛いくらい握って離さない
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.56,0:28:28.20,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}わがままな今連れて　誰のものでもない未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.20,0:28:30.90,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}そこから始めるの
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.90,0:28:41.46,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}空を掴む(夢の欠片)　祈りの手を(指先まで)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.46,0:28:46.53,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}伸ばすかぎり(生けるかぎり)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.53,0:28:54.60,ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}そこに本当はあるの
Comment: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:20.52,ed ch,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.86,0:27:46.63,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}小心翼翼地温柔抱着 使它流下熔化的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.20,0:27:57.83,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}我可沒法成為那樣的冰雪人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.26,0:28:12.06,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}我再也不會逃避 我想要知道變強的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.06,0:28:13.76,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.76,0:28:17.86,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}將第一個約定的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.86,0:28:22.26,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}緊握到疼痛 絕不放開
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.56,0:28:28.20,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}帶着任性的現在 前往不屬於任何人的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.20,0:28:30.90,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}從那裏開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.90,0:28:41.46,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}抓緊天空(夢想的碎片) 祈願的手(直到指尖)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.46,0:28:46.53,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}只要還能夠伸出(只要仍活着)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.53,0:28:54.60,ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3)}那裏就會有真物在
